name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
	t1.`BRANCH`,
	t1.`DELETED`,
	t1.`GRADE`,
	t1.`ID`,
	CONCAT( '/', t1.`name` ) AS `NAME`,
	t1.`ORDER`,
	t1.`OWNER`,
	case when t1.`PARENT` = 0 then null else t1.parent end as parent ,
	t11.`NAME` AS `PARENTNAME`,
	t1.`PATH`,
	t1.`ROOT`,
	t1.`SHORT`,
	t1.`TYPE`,
	t1.MODULESN
FROM
	`zt_module` t1
	LEFT JOIN zt_module t11 ON t1.PARENT = t11.ID
